CHANGES IN VERSION 1.28.0
------------------------

Notes

    o Fix build error on Windows and Mac.

CHANGES IN VERSION 1.17.1
------------------------

Notes

    o Fix a small bug in function methodsMerge.

CHANGES IN VERSION 1.17.0
------------------------

Notes

    o Update to the latest version of different tools.


CHANGES IN VERSION 1.7.1
------------------------

Notes

    o Fixed a bug in svAnnotation.

CHANGES IN VERSION 1.2.0
------------------------

Notes

    o Add support to SV prediction programs Lumpy
      and softSearch.
    o Modify methodsMerge to make it more robust.
    o Modify all the read functions to coordinate
      methodsMerge.


CHANGES IN VERSION 1.1.4
------------------------

Notes

    o Modify svAnnotation and geneAnnotation to deal with
      more versatile genome annotation files.
    o Modify plotChromosome to deal with exceptions.

CHANGES IN VERSION 1.1.3
------------------------

Notes

    o Modify readDelly and readSvseq to deal with
      exceptions in the output of SV prediction programs.
    o Add more parameters to the function 'methodsMerge' to 
      make it more robust.


CHANGES IN VERSION 1.1.2
------------------------

Notes

    o Modify readPindel and readBreakDancer to deal with
      exceptions in the output of SV prediction programs.


CHANGES IN VERSION 1.0.1
------------------------

Notes

    o Add more parameters to the function 'methodsMerge' to 
      accept user defined thresholds.


CHANGES IN VERSION 0.99.3
------------------------

Notes

    o Improvement of the vigenette to make it more comprehensive.
    o Removal of useless example dataset.
      
      




